&lt;section class="flex center f-col br-secondary"&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;Evento Scroll&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Haz un scroll y despu√©s espera 1 seg &lt;span id="scroll"&gt;Scrolleando...&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;/section&gt;</code></pre>
